<h3 id="usecase-diagram">UseCase Diagram</h3>
<ul>
  <li>This is used to capture the dynamic aspects of system.</li>
  <li>Use cases have
    <ul>
      <li>Actors</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Usecases represent high level activities</li>
  <li>Lets draw a use case diagram for Bank Atm, we have 3 types of users
    <ol>
      <li>Customer: Uses atm for
        <ul>
          <li>Checking balances</li>
          <li>Deposit funds</li>
          <li>Withdraws funds</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Cashier
        <ul>
          <li>Deposit amount into ATM</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Admin/Technician:
        <ul>
          <li>Maintenance</li>
          <li>Repair</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </li>
</ul>

